Citigroup

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search

Not to be confused with CIT Group or CITIC Group.
"Citi" redirects here. For the bus service in the British cities Cambridge, Peterborough, Preston and Gloucester, see Stagecoach Group. For the car, see Volkswagen Citi Golf.

